      <description>&lt;p&gt;slug: The-Coolest-Thing-I-ve-Ever-Done&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;the-coolest-thing-ive-ever-done-building-an-ai-learning-tool-for-visually-impaired-children&#34;&gt;The Coolest Thing I&amp;rsquo;ve Ever Done: Building an AI Learning Tool for Visually Impaired Children&lt;a href=&#34;#the-coolest-thing-ive-ever-done-building-an-ai-learning-tool-for-visually-impaired-children&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;By Ezra Wu | April 5, 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-beginning-a-spark-of-an-idea&#34;&gt;The Beginning: A Spark of an Idea&lt;a href=&#34;#the-beginning-a-spark-of-an-idea&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;In October 2024, I saw the announcement for the &lt;strong&gt;Microsoft Imagine Cup&lt;/strong&gt;. A thought flashed through my mind: &lt;em&gt;What if we could really use technology to change the world?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
